4. Call Data (Most Essential)
-To simulate call data we need to create 5-10 network outage events. To show case this in the data we need surge of calls in a certain time frame. We already have the call transcripts generated, but we need to map them to the customer data within the proper distribution
 For example:
Outage in CA, Murrieta, 92562 started on 11/16/2025 at 10 AM. We should have surge of calls from the customers in the region from 10 am to 11 am Most of the time customer will call in the first hour of the outages and 
the volume will drop later on. So we need to fill the fake data in the datetime column accordingly.

- Transcripts: We would require variety of transcripts with various issues. But the transcript talking about outages should be concentrated between the outage time frame to simulate the reality in synthetic data.


